- SEBI is unable to satisfy itself that its suspicion regarding wrongdoing - Hence the Committee is unable to conclude wrongdoing as not enough information forthcoming via SEBI investigation.
In the same report it says LIC was the largest buyer of Adani’s 4.8 crore shares when the price shot from ₹ 1031 to ₹ 3859.
At whose behest?
Also, this committee was to investigate regulatory failures to check stock manipulation which again has been opaque. So what are they celebrating exactly?
